snippet.title: Word Worth GameplayVideo ***NEW RELEASE*** 2018
snippet.description: Step into the mysterious "Cave of Words" and create as many 3 - 8 letter words are you can using the colorgul gems before time runs out! Discover what your Words are Worth today! An addictive, challenging, uniquely intense, exciting new word game developed by Whata Hoot Game Designs, LLC. Enjoy!
